Rating: 2
This was good but not amazing or anything. I love the hazel nut oil it contains. I will be using the oil from this recipe in salad dressings and other recipes, that oil is good stuff. I served the dip at thanksgiving as an appetizer and people liked it but didn't rave or anything. I'm not sure If I'd make it again.

