Rating: 4
This was quick, easy, and delicious. Definitely one one the best dips I've had. I am serving it with pesto pita chips. The only down side is the few ingredients are quite expensive if you don't already have them, especially the walnut oil. Worth it though.

Rating: 4
This recipe is fantastic! Using a baguette helped out the texture. I doubled the cumin and pepper, and cut the salt in half, and it was easily the best dip I have ever served. This also makes a great sandwich spread! This will absolutely be a regular addition to my menu